{"tid":1029253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【向鹹網宣戰】色情業經濟效益不容忽視 以美國計年賺至少$390億","createTime":"2019-02-20T06:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T12:44:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05891f77e26293a325c941b7a635ce1df0c8aec1","tid":1029253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190220/large/1550638567_b6b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190220%2Flarge%2F1550638567_b6b6.jpg&h=61f467c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n色情工業龐大，帶來的經濟效益不容忽視，有業界調查公司保守估計，單是美國色情業已年賺50億美元（390億港元），而其他服務亦會因為色情業暢旺而有所得益。<br />\n<br />\n專門報道色情業動向的出版商XBIZ在2012年一項調查估計，業界一年收入高達50億美元，有關數字至2018年更會增至超過60億美元（468億港元）。XBIZ創辦人赫曼（Alec Helmy）指，由於色情業私隱度高，加上大部份公司都是私人擁有，欠缺公開數據作出準確評估，有分析甚至認為業界一年收入或高達150億美元（1,170億港元）。<br />\n無論是60億美元或是150億，色情業佔娛樂經濟的比重不輕，作為對比，《Quartz》整理娛樂業去年的收入預測，例如NBA一年收入為74億，而美式足球的一年收入則為140億美元（1,092億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯2012年曾規定成人影片演員不可「打真軍」演出後，緊接4年的拍攝色情影片許可申請大跌95%；同期拉斯維加斯因容許演員不戴安全套上陣，色情片生產數量在2012至2013年間大增50%。加州2016年有議員提出表決，要求全州色情片演員使用安全套演出，當時州務卿及無黨派的議員都警告，如果這法案成為法律，州政府及地方政府每年將減少數百萬計美元稅收。<br />\n此外，諸如像AT&amp;T的電訊服務運營商、像DirecTV的衞星電視服務供應商，以及像萬豪的連鎖酒店等等，都間接受惠色情業並有數以百萬計美元收入。有AT&amp;T人員曾向《紐約時報》形容：「每個人都知道這情況，但你不能說什麼。」與此同時，民眾足不出戶就可在家享受成人娛樂，亦有助推動科技應用，如更快接受電子信用卡交易、即時通訊、串流以至VR（虛擬實境）技術等等。"},{"pid":"698e5ceb9245496dd8f151937433b716f8bc31ce","tid":1029253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:09:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190220/59281028?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F59281028%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n89qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=1130977e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F59281028%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&h=309b25a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190220/59281028?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2</a>"},{"pid":"6ef89e08d7d4054f4882a14507934cc5136ccb76","tid":1029253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0fdc2ba8e0932c0d2675055db3fe488a7f1b79","tid":1029253,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"加快科技發展<br />\n<br />\n無咸網 唔駛5g唔駛4K"},{"pid":"af0015accad0db0ac4dfa60929cad7d4b930d356","tid":1029253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a163fb52707c410718325a4fc010a7aa699b15","tid":1029253,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b0fdc2ba8e0932c0d2675055db3fe488a7f1b79","tid":1029253,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"加快科技發展<br />\n<br />\n無咸網 唔駛5g唔駛4K"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:26:34.000Z","msg":"無av都唔知幾時有1080<br />\n仲話4k<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a0354287c3ecfae566177b68a8e5187092a439","tid":1029253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}